    "Nook checks for new articles in the background and sends a notification when some arrive. iOS decides exactly when to run this, so timing is approximate." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nook checks for new articles in the background and sends a notification when some arrive. iOS decides exactly when to run this, so timing is approximate."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nook がバックグラウンドで新着記事を確認し、届いたら通知します。実行タイミングは iOS が決めるため、時間は目安です。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nook이 백그라운드에서 새 글을 확인하고 도착하면 알림을 보냅니다. 실행 시점은 iOS가 정하므로 시간은 대략적입니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nook 会在后台检查新文章并在有更新时发送通知。具体运行时间由 iOS 决定，因此时间为大致值。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Nook Feedback" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nook Feedback"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
